    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to organizational, regulatory, or representative bodies for particular trades or occupations. These may promote and develop commercial and industrial interests, or advocate for the views of members on matters of common interest.</Note_Text>
